            <title>[AMQ-3085] IndexOutOfBoundsException on FailoverTransport.updateURIs after: already known: java.net.UnknownHostException</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-3085</link>
                <project id="12311210" key="AMQ">ActiveMQ Classic</project>
